main event: A businessman driving home saw two saucer-shaped objects traveling in a south-north direction, though they were shrouded in steam.
interesting points: The objects were seen by a businessman driving home with his family after spending a day in the country.
The objects were described as saucer-shaped and traveling at a high velocity.
The objects were shrouded in steam, making it difficult to see them clearly.
The objects were observed in the Alicante, Spain area on July 22, 1965.
This incident was reported in the AFRO Bulletin from September-October 1965.
